  "slug": "soft-and-chewy-oatmeal-raisin-cookies",
  "title": "Soft and Chewy Oatmeal Raisin Cookies",
  "subtitle": "Crisp at the edges, soft in the middle.",
  "excerpt": "Soft and Chewy Oatmeal Raisin Cookies. A baking recipe from Rebecca's collection, straightforward, reliable, worth weighing rather than scooping.",
  "type": "RECIPE",
  "sourceNotes": "From Rebecca's personal cookbook, a recipe she's made many times in her own kitchen.",
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Soft and Chewy Oatmeal Raisin Cookies. An American family-table recipe, generous, comforting, built for a crowd. Adjustable for what you need.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Cookies bake fast and reward a chilled dough. Pull them out when the edges set and the middles still look slightly underdone.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
